data.description: Property sits on the end of a cull de sac and overlook a pond with fish in it, The home will be turnkey as owners only taking personal items. As you walk up to the door you will notice  professional looking landscape and than to left a patio. Entering you will look to right and see an office that used to be a courtyard to your left the kitchen and going forward to the living room with its cathedral cedar ceiling and the room has been expanded by 10 feet. The home is ready to move into and has a single car garage. Located not far from the community pooland great aea for walking or biking. Call for an appointment as it should not last long. This being sold fully furnished less personal items
